{"tid":1490771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪已經原諒咗警察呢 ?","createTime":"2019-08-20T08:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:15:43.000Z","uid":125079,"like":92,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"4272f5f5206e8bb4b9cb8fe7bff769ebe735967c","tid":1490771,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"林鄭想用今日依兩單野洗黑警底<br />\n<br />\n洗你條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死黑警 不得好死<br />\n<br />\n如果冇片, 個幾隻警狗用私刑單野永遠冇人知<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係將軍澳市民琴晚自發洗樓, 搵人, 搵到證據, 班狗連做野都冇打算做 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好話比我聽有人真係因為依兩單野已咁快被感化<br />\n<br />\n612 恐襲 721 元朗黑社會黑警合作<br />\n811 香港最黑暗既一日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有無數無數前線手足被濫捕 被虐待 被控告</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有我地一路依接近三個月既付出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可 重申一次</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 撒回送中惡法<br />\n2. 撤銷對義士的檢控<br />\n3. 撤回暴動性質<br />\n4. 獨立調查委員會 ( 已經要變重組警隊 )<br />\n5. 真普選"},{"pid":"b2a10df7f33c8d5a4755881417e8d953caf869fd","tid":1490771,"uid":255976,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"凸，無得原諒！"},{"pid":"6532bacefd88933ccc6871c87ee3fff5d66a8793","tid":1490771,"uid":28831,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"一世都冇可能原諒<br />\n如果今次黑警都洗到底我之後都去做黑警"},{"pid":"9943b5431bea8efe7aad615c285d2b295daa7f95","tid":1490771,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"c0a3adf6de7fa15d6244dab38283f21adce1d307","tid":1490771,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"邊個原諒咗既入黎<br />\n<br />\n你對唔對得住犧牲咗咁多野 幫我地一路撐到依一刻既每一個人"},{"pid":"09977ed716038bd9ff40da9325422a18ac65bf76","tid":1490771,"uid":62776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:03:04.000Z","msg":"佢地死撚晒我咪原諒佢地囉<